_sText:
It's my first map, so bear with me.

Anyhows, this map is made of three floors, teleporters, an invisible wall, and some weapon machines. There is one hidden item, but I'll let you figure that out for yourselves.

This is still in beta, so there are bound to be a few errors and bugs here and there, but me and some friends are testing the map as I type this, so these bugs will be found and erased quite fast.

That's all I got to say, have fun!

0.2: Fix'd some bugs where people spawned at the same place
